  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>A Call of Duty movie is set to release on 30th June, 2028. Yellowstone's Taylor Sheridan and Battleship's Pete Berg will be writing and directing the flick, respectively.</p>
<p>Announced during a CinemaCon presentation yesterday, head of Activision and producer on the film Rob Kostich said: "I told everyone we were only going to make a movie if it's right. In David Ellison, we found that partnership [...] We want to make sure that the authenticity of it is captured on a human level so that it feels really real and infuses that with epic scope."</p>

